2021年11月9日，韓國媒體《Singlelist》報導稱《Running Man向前衝》將於11月12日首播。<ref>{{cite news|language=ko|author=강보라|url=http://www.slist.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=309320|title='런닝맨: 뛰는 놈 위에 노는 놈' 11월 12일 공개 확정(공식)|publisher=Singlelist|date=2021-11-09|accessdate=2021-11-09|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109052459/http://www.slist.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=309320}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language=ko|author=전효진|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000943722|title=디즈니+ ‘런닝맨: 뛰는 놈 위에 노는 놈’ 11월 12일 공개 [공식]|publisher=Sports Donga|date=2021-11-09|accessdate=2021-11-09|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109083646/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000943722}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language=ko|author=박수인|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/609/0000508795|title=‘런닝맨: 뛰는 놈 위에 노는 놈’ 12일 첫 공개, 수트 차려입은 김종국 하하 지석진|publisher=Newsen|date=2021-11-09|accessdate=2021-11-09|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109202510/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/609/0000508795}}</ref>

